stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> TokenInput

    TokenInput --> ConfidentPrediction: H ≤ 0.583 OR c ≥ 0.787

    TokenInput --> UncertainPrediction: H > 0.583 AND c < 0.787

    UncertainPrediction --> EntityFilter

    EntityFilter --> BlockedEntity: GIVENNAME, SURNAME, CITY...
    EntityFilter --> RoutableEntity: CREDITCARD, PHONE, EMAIL...

    BlockedEntity --> ConfidentPrediction

    RoutableEntity --> LLMQuery

    LLMQuery --> ValidBIO: BIO constraints satisfied
    LLMQuery --> InvalidBIO: BIO constraints violated

    InvalidBIO --> ConfidentPrediction

    ValidBIO --> LLMCorrectedOutput

    ConfidentPrediction --> [*]
    LLMCorrectedOutput --> [*]
